body:
Thanks @igordertigor for checking! 
Could you also check the pip version on travis?

Looking at the error , our binary might be built against a higher version of glibc than the ones you have. Please refer to [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/5033#issuecomment-263681255) for more details 

Is it possible to upgrade them on your system?
